255
0:09:52.083,000 --> 0:09:53,000
To take a different path.

256
0:09:53.958,000 --> 0:09:55,000
Here we are on Earth.

257
0:09:56.458,000 --> 0:09:58,000
And life on Earth is a wonderful thing.

258
0:09:59.083,000 --> 0:10:,000
